CIDR --> Classless Inter Domain Routing --> Range of IP addresses

VPC --> CIDR --> 172.31.0.0/16

172.31.0.0 --> Base IP
/16 --> Subnet Mask

1. How many IP addresses? 32 - 16 = 16 --> 2^16

172.31.0.0/24 --> Total number of IP addresses --> 256

